dc_title_s: Johnson's Michigan and Wisconsin; by Johnson and Ward.
dc_description_s: Prime meridians at Greenwich and Washington. Includes view of Straits of Mackinaw. Probably detached from an atlas by Alvin J. Johnson, no. 45-46. In upper left margin: 45. In upper right margin: 46. 1 map: hand colored; 44 x 57 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
